      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/snb-chairman-says-further-interest-rate-cuts-could-be-necessary-2024-10-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[瑞士央行行长马丁施莱格尔周二表示，瑞士央行可能进一步降息以维持价格稳定。]]></description>
