      <title>由于波兰抵押贷款规定，Raiffeisen 下调股本回报率预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/raiffeisen-cuts-roe-guidance-polish-mortgage-loans-provisions-2024-10-29/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[奥地利莱夫艾森国际银行（RBI）周二表示，该行已下调今年的股本回报率（ROE）预期，但不包括俄罗斯和白俄罗斯业务。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/raiffeisen-cuts-roe-guidance-polish-mortgage-loans-provisions-2024-10-29/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:33:29 GMT</pubDate>
